#: ../../analysis/peak.rst:142
msgid ""
"Line shapes are added to the fitting model by clicking the buttons "
"labeled :button:`Add step,light` or :button:`Add peak,light`. The "
"functional form of the lineshape is chosen by selection from the menu to "
"the left of those buttons."
